---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="收到了" description="諮詢表單送出成功">
  <article class="max-w-xl mx-auto px-6 py-24 text-center">
    <header class="eyebrow-pair justify-center">
      <span class="ey-left">已收到您的訊息</span>
    </header>
    <h1 class="font-display text-ink mt-2 leading-tight tracking-[-0.02em]" style="font-size: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 5rem);">
      <em class="italic text-teal">謝謝</em>。
    </h1>
    <p class="font-serif text-base text-ink mt-6 leading-relaxed">
      我會在 1–2 個工作日內回信。如果適合進一步聊，會附上 Google Calendar 預約連結。
    </p>
    <a href="/" class="btn-ghost mt-8">回首頁</a>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
